data.meta_description: We offer FOCUS wall mounted units in various cooling and heating capacities, making it easy to choose the right solution to fit your needs. The outdoor units are supplied separately..
data.text:
These are cookies that are essential for the functioning of our website, are always used and cannot be disabled. These cookies do not store any personal information that would help us to identify you. They function in response to actions you take within our website such as logging in to your profile, completing a questionnaire etc.

The legal basis for the processing of these cookies is our legitimate interests.

This type of cookie helps us to improve the performance of our website as it allows us to count visits and traffic sources. They help to determine the visit rate and therefore the popularity of different parts of the website. All data collected by these cookies is completely anonymous. It is possible to disable this type of cookie on our website and if you do, we will not keep track of when you visited our website or what specific parts of our website you visited.

The legal basis for the processing of these cookies is your voluntary consent, which you can withdraw at any time.

These cookies are used to create the best possible profile of your interests and the subsequent display of advertising messages based on your preferences, including contacting you with marketing offers where appropriate. These cookies may be shared with other recipients of personal data to create a profile of your interests in order to display relevant advertising on other websites.

These cookies work on the basis of the unique identification of your device and internet browser. If you do not allow this type of cookie, the advertising messages will be less targeted and may not correspond to your interests.

The legal basis for the processing of these cookies is your voluntary consent, which you can withdraw at any time.
